CHANGELING

Changelings are shapeshifting humanoids with the natural ability to mimic
the appearance of any person or creature of similar size.  On Rifts Earth
they are rare and often paranoid: they live in a world that shoots first
and classifies later, and an unknown shapeshifter tends to get both.
Those who master their gift become excellent infiltrators, diplomats, and spies.

ATTRIBUTES (approximate ranges):
  IQ: 3-18   ME: 3-18   MA: 5-20   PS: 3-18
  PP: 3-18   PE: 3-18   PB: 6-26   Spd: 3-18

DAMAGE POOL:
  SDC: 1d6 x10 + PE (approx 10-60 + PE)

SPECIAL ABILITIES:
  - Shapeshift into any humanoid of similar size
  - Natural mimic: can copy voices and mannerisms
  - Exceptional PB in natural form
  - Enhanced MA: socially adept

PENALTIES:
  - If true nature revealed, may face violent reactions
  - Some psychics can detect the shapeshifting regardless of form

OCC ELIGIBLE: Yes.
ALIGNMENT: Any.

